# Regenerable pipeline layers — not source, not the served artifact.
# 01_raw is re-fetched from Rebrickable weekly (pipeline/fetch_rebrickable.py) —
# committing a fresh ~50MB+ dump every run would balloon repo size for no
# benefit, so it's excluded like the other regenerable layers even though it's
# nominally "raw" rather than derived. See issue #14.
